      <title>摩根大通盈利后出售 80 亿美元公司债券</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-15/jpmorgan-kicks-off-post-earnings-borrowing-binge-for-big-banks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[摩根大通公司在周五公布业绩后，于周二发售价值 80 亿美元的美国投资级公司债券，为华尔街顶级银行可能大举发行债券奠定基础。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-15/jpmorgan-kicks-off-post-earnings-borrowing-binge-for-big-banks</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 15 Oct 2024 12:50:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>报道称以色列不会针对伊朗原油 油价暴跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-14/oil-drops-at-open-on-report-israel-won-t-attack-iranian-crude</link>
      <description><![CDATA[有报道称，以色列可能不会瞄准伊朗的原油基础设施，这缓解了人们对潜在供应中断的担忧，导致油价暴跌，交易商的注意力重新转向对明年初原油供应大幅过剩的预期。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-14/oil-drops-at-open-on-report-israel-won-t-attack-iranian-crude</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 14 Oct 2024 22:02:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
